{Religion}
My Church is called Salem Hall.It is an Evangelical Church.About 60 to 80 people go a week.There is a Breaking of Bread Service at 10.30 to 11.30. At 12.00 there is a Sunday School class and there is a service in the evening at 6.30.There is a Coventers class where people from the age of 12-20 and so on, go while we're at Sunday School.
